Description: vigicaen provides a set of tools to facilitate the analysis of the 
       VigiBase Extract Case Level dataset e.g., load data, perform data management,
       disproportionality analysis, and descriptive statistics. The package is designed
       to be used in the context of pharmacovigilance studies. 
       VigiBase Extract Case Level is the World Health Organization (WHO) 
       global individual case safety reports (ICSRs) database, maintained by
       the Uppsala Monitoring Centre, Sweden.
       This package is NOT supported nor reflect the opinion of the WHO, or the
       Uppsala Monitoring Centre.
